# work on some other existing other's project
fork the directory in your git space
then go to the command line and type 
git clone https://github.com/Soumeniisc/directory_that_forked.git
git branch -a
git branch novclassfeature
git checkout novclassfeature
gedit file.txt
git status
git add file.txt
git commit -m "massage"
git push -u origin novclassfeature
#branch novclassfeature set up to track remote branch novclassfeature from origin
if you do "git checkout master" then you will see that newly created file will no longer be  there in the filder anymore.
# EGit is an Eclipse Team provider for the Git version control system. The EGit project is implementing Eclipse tooling on top of the JGit Java implementation of Git.

File attachments on issues and pull requests
--------------------------------------------
To attach a file to an issue or pull request conversation, drag and drop it into the comment box.

The maximum size for files is 25MB and the maximum size for images is 10MB.

